productData.Name: Creed Aventus Eau de Parfum
productData.Description: Aventus celebrates strength, vision and success, inspired by the dramatic life of war, peace and romance lived by Emperor Napoleon. The bottle is emblazoned with a silver emblem of a horse and rider.

productData.Name: Chanel No. 5
productData.Description: A bouquet of abstract flowers with an indefinable femininity.

productData.Name: CK One
productData.Description: This fragrance carries fresh notes of green tea while embracing the sweetness of amber and musk.

productData.Name: Dior Sauvage Eau de Toilette
productData.Description: Inspired by wide-open spaces, Sauvage is an ozone-blue sky sprawled above a rocky landscape, white-hot beneath the desert sun.

productData.Name: Tom Ford Black Orchid Eau de Parfum
productData.Description: A luxurious and sensual fragrance of rich, dark accords and an alluring potion of black orchids and spice.
